      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">MODIFYING AND CHANGING PRIVACY POLICY</h3>
      <p>We reserve the right to update this policy at any time without prior notice. Your continued use constitutes acceptance.</p>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">CONTACT US</h3>
      <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, contact us at: <a class="text-primary" href="mailto:info@yastech.com.sa">info@yastech.com.sa</a></p>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>


